{"tid":1395102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 pepe正式加盟阿記","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:49:01.000Z","uid":153600,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"90cb89af019662bc9433a4b218fddc0d39b51cbc","tid":1395102,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"Arsenal have signed Ivory Coast winger Nicolas Pepe from Lille for a club record fee of &pound;72m.<br />\nThe 24-year-old has signed a five-year contract at Emirates Stadium after having a medical on Tuesday.<br />\nPepe scored 35 goals in 74 Ligue 1 appearances for Lille, who he joined from Angers in 2017.<br />\n&quot;Nicolas is a highly rated and talented winger who was wanted by many of the top teams in Europe,&quot; said Gunners boss Unai Emery.<br />\n&quot;Signing a top-class winger has been one of our key objectives in this transfer window and I'm delighted he's joining.<br />\n&quot;He will add pace, power and creativity, with the aim of bringing more goals to our team.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nMore to follow."},{"pid":"b31541428e856a41d9d3b9e39e32ffcb451c0d23","tid":1395102,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c6fb0d0f6c6c2fd138a61252592da14320f22d","tid":1395102,"uid":5649,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"成堆黑鬼喺前場認能死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee6f4b8db20ff04abe3f0fa45fb9fbb97597c6c","tid":1395102,"uid":77355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b31541428e856a41d9d3b9e39e32ffcb451c0d23","tid":1395102,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"72m 分幾多期"},{"pid":"ebfb31b9